$ ORA-01045: user ... lacks CREATE SESSION privilege; logon denied
 		
  This error is thrown if a user wants to log on a database but lacks the 
    → http://www.adp-gmbh.ch/ora/admin/system_privileges.html#create_session[create session] → http://www.adp-gmbh.ch/ora/misc/users_roles_privs.html#system_privileges[system privilege].

  The required privilege can be given with a
code {
→ development/databases/Oracle/SQL/DCL/grant create session to the_user;
code }

sa:
  Other → http://www.adp-gmbh.ch/ora/err/index.html[Oracle error messages].
  
